text: Protochnoye () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Protochensky Selsoviet, Limansky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 610 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 100 km from Astrakhan, 31 km from Liman. == References == Category:Rural localities in Limansky District
title: Protochnoye
